index.heading: Life isn’t about getting and having, it’s about giving and being.
index.subheading: Life isn’t about getting and having, it’s about giving and being.
index.discription: Obesity is the largest epidemic worldwide that reportedly kills people of all ages. This deadly disease currently affects more than 2 billion people worldwide. Due to changing food systems and reduced physical activity, this disease has been spreading rapidly.
